[src:aws-cloudformation/provisioning-technology] The provisioning software will capture each circuit number provided by all of your carriers and if billing occurs outside of the contracted rate an exception rule will trigger a red flag and notify the pre-established staff member to review the billing error.
[src:aws-cloudformation/provisioning-technology] Server provisioning is a set of actions to prepare a server with appropriate systems, data and software, and make it ready for network operation.
[src:aws-cloudformation/provisioning-technology] By auditing the system, you ensure OVAL compliance with limit vulnerability, ensure compliance, or install patches.
[src:aws-cloudformation/provisioning-technology] After these actions, you restart the system and load the new software.
[src:aws-cloudformation/provisioning-technology] This makes the system ready for operation.
